@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<style>
    /* In-doc embedded style sheet for this view */
    body {
        background-color: #3b3f3f; /* Lightened Gunmetal background color */
        color: #ffffff; /* White text color */
    }

    .text-center h1 {
        color: #f46516; /* Orange Pantone for headings */
    }

    .text-center p {
        color: #ffffff; /* White text color for paragraphs */
    }

    .text-center h2 {
        color: #0a9d9b; /* Dark Cyan for subheadings */
    }
</style>

<div class="text-center">
    <h1 class="text-center">Privacy Policy</h1> <!-- Main heading for the Privacy Policy -->

    <p class="text-center">
        At ABC Retail, we are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring that your personal information is handled in a safe and responsible manner. This Privacy Policy outlines the types of information we collect, how we use and protect it, and your rights regarding your personal data.
    </p> <!-- Introduction paragraph -->

    <h2 class="text-center">1. Information We Collect</h2> <!-- Subheading for information collection section -->
    <p class="text-center">
        We may collect personal information from you when you visit our site, register an account, or place an order. This information may include your name, email address, phone number, and shipping address.
    </p> <!-- Paragraph detailing the information collected -->

    <h2 class="text-center">2. How We Use Your Information</h2> <!-- Subheading for information usage section -->
    <p class="text-center">
        The information we collect is used to process your orders, provide customer service, and send you updates on your order status. We may also use your information to improve our website, send promotional emails, or conduct surveys.
    </p> <!-- Paragraph detailing how the information is used -->

    <h2 class="text-center">3. Protecting Your Information</h2> <!-- Subheading for information protection section -->
    <p class="text-center">
        We implement a variety of security measures to ensure the safety of your personal information. These measures include secure servers, encrypted payment gateways, and strict access controls. We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personal information to outside parties.
    </p> <!-- Paragraph detailing how the information is protected -->

    <h2 class="text-center">4. Your Rights</h2> <!-- Subheading for user rights section -->
    <p class="text-center">
        You have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal information at any time. You can do this by logging into your account or contacting our customer service team. If you wish to unsubscribe from our marketing communications, you can do so by following the unsubscribe link in any email we send.
    </p> <!-- Paragraph detailing user rights -->

    <h2 class="text-center">5. Changes to This Policy</h2> <!-- Subheading for policy changes section -->
    <p class="text-center">
        We reserve the right to update or change this Privacy Policy at any time. Any changes will be posted on this page, and we encourage you to review our policy periodically to stay informed of how we are protecting your information.
    </p> <!-- Paragraph detailing policy change notifications -->

    <p class="text-center">If you have any questions about our Privacy Policy, please contact us at <strong>abc@support.co.za</strong> or <strong>011 682 7901</strong>.</p> <!-- Contact information paragraph -->

</div>